author: seelmann
msg: DIRSTUDIO-1041: Headless run of SWTBot tests
* Extend ApacheDS framework runner to capture screenshot of failing tests
* Replace some hand-written wait conditions by SWTBot provided
* Wait till wizards and dialogs are closed to avoid timeouts and race conditions
* Monitor and wait till background jobs are finished to avoid timeouts and race conditions

author: desruisseaux
msg: Feature: initial support of parameterless operations used as "virtual attribute".
Existing tests continue to pass, new tests still need to be written for the new capability.
